<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Wulong</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-15 05:13:14</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Having a pair of batons is really nice below 40.  But once you hit 40 your fists start to do some crazy damages.  I stopped using my baton at about 43 or or so.  I have seen 45+ monks still using batons.  Give your fists a chance; use them sometimes and you will see how nice they are.  Right now my hands hits about twice as hard.<BR>
They are quite common now, and i have seen them sell for 1000-1100 plats.<BR>
I would much rather have a pair of knuckle dusters or canes of tranquil.</font></td></tr></table>
